## 🗄️ DATABASE SCHEMA

### contacts
```sql
id, channel (whatsapp|instagram), channel_id, name, avatar_url, tags (json), notes, timestamps
```

### conversations
```sql
id, contact_id, channel, status (open|resolved|pending|needs_human),
ai_enabled (boolean), last_message_at, unread_count, timestamps
```

### messages
```sql
id, conversation_id, direction (inbound|outbound), content,
message_type (text|image|audio|order_detected),
sent_by (ai|human), raw_payload (json), timestamps
```

### orders
```sql
id, conversation_id, contact_id, items (json), total_estimated,
status (detected|confirmed|cancelled), raw_text, timestamps
```

### business_settings
```sql
id, key, value (text), group (ai_prompt|channel|general)
```

