## 🚀 URUTAN DEVELOPMENT

### Phase 1 — Foundation
1. Setup Laravel 12 + Inertia + Vue 3 + Tailwind
2. Migrations: contacts, conversations, messages, orders, business_settings
3. Models + relationships
4. Setup Redis + Laravel Horizon
5. Setup Soketi untuk realtime

### Phase 2 — Core Engine
6. WebhookController untuk WhatsApp
7. ProcessIncomingMessage job
8. AIAgentService (Claude API integration)
9. WhatsAppService (kirim reply)
10. Test end-to-end

### Phase 3 — Frontend MVP
11. Layout utama (sidebar + main)
12. Inbox/Index.vue
13. Inbox/Show.vue + realtime
14. Toggle AI per conversation
15. Manual reply form

### Phase 4 — Instagram + Orders
16. InstagramService + webhook
17. Orders/Index.vue
18. Settings/Index.vue

### Phase 5 — Polish & Launch
19. README lengkap (English + Indonesia)
20. docker-compose.yml
21. GitHub Actions CI
22. Demo GIF + screenshots
23. Launch ke komunitas
